name: ΚΚlwMW
statement: theorem ΚΚlwMW (a b : Η0Ja) : νΦΗ (ΚxΝ a b) oVΟ = ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (νΦΗ a oVΟ) (νΦΗ b oVΟ)) (ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b) := by
proof:
theorem ΚΚlwMW (a b : Η0Ja) : νΦΗ (ΚxΝ a b) oVΟ = ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (νΦΗ a oVΟ) (νΦΗ b oVΟ)) (ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b) := by
  -- Simplify all νΦΗ _ oVΟ terms using ΓpKΚYδω
  rw [ΓpKΚYδω, ΓpKΚYδω, ΓpKΚYδω]
  -- Left side is now ΕWβ (ΚxΝ a b) (ΚxΝ a b)
  -- Right side is ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a a) (ΕWβ b b)) (ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b)
  
  -- Expand left side using eexzzm_
  rw [eexzzm_]
  -- Now left side is ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a (ΚxΝ a b)) (ΕWβ b (ΚxΝ a b))
  
  -- Expand ΕWβ a (ΚxΝ a b) using Ωψ'YiΑσ
  rw [Ωψ'YiΑσ]
  -- Expand ΕWβ b (ΚxΝ a b) using Ωψ'YiΑσ
  rw [Ωψ'YiΑσ]
  
  -- Now we have:
  -- Left: ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a a) (ΕWβ a b)) (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ b a) (ΕWβ b b))
  -- Right: ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a a) (ΕWβ b b)) (ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b)
  
  -- Use commutativity of ΚxΝ (KΩΦzαυωT) and associativity (nv3ΧWtℕsL) to rearrange
  -- First group terms appropriately
  rw [KΩΦzαυωT (ΕWβ a b), KΩΦzαυωT (ΕWβ b a)]
  rw [← nv3ΧWtℕsL, ← nv3ΧWtℕsL]
  
  -- Now we need to show ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b = ΕWβ a b
  -- From theorem Ν_zivκyA: ΕWβ (Θ7Κr a) b = ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a b) b
  -- But oVΟ is Θ7Κr gfΧ, so ΕWβ oVΟ a = ΕWβ (Θ7Κr gfΧ) a = ΚxΝ (ΕWβ gfΧ a) a
  -- Then ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b = ΕWβ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ gfΧ a) a) b
  -- This seems complicated - perhaps there's a simpler approach
  
  -- Alternative approach: use ℝzΗσℝcψ which says ΕWβ gfΧ m = m
  -- So ΕWβ gfΧ a = a
  -- Then ΕWβ oVΟ a = ΕWβ (Θ7Κr gfΧ) a = ΚxΝ (ΕWβ gfΧ a) a = ΚxΝ a a
  -- Then ΕWβ (ΕWβ oVΟ a) b = ΕWβ (ΚxΝ a a) b = ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a b) (ΕWβ a b)
  -- This doesn't seem to match what we need
  
  -- Perhaps better to use the theorem ΙΦΔVfe9: ΕWβ oVΟ m = ΚxΝ m m
  rw [ΙΦΔVfe9]  -- ΕWβ oVΟ a = ΚxΝ a a
  rw [ΙΦΔVfe9]  -- ΕWβ (ΚxΝ a a) b = ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a b) (ΕWβ a b)
  
  -- Now right side has ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a a) (ΕWβ b b)) (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a b) (ΕWβ a b))
  -- Left side is ΚxΝ (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a a) (ΕWβ a b)) (ΚxΝ (ΕWβ a b) (ΕWβ b b))
  
  -- These are equal by commutativity and associativity of ΚxΝ
  rw [KΩΦzαυωT (ΕWβ a b), ← nv3ΧWtℕsL, nv3ΧWtℕsL]
  rw [KΩΦzαυωT (ΕWβ b b), nv3ΧWtℕsL]
  rw [KΩΦzαυωT (ΕWβ a b), nv3ΧWtℕsL]
  rfl
